{
  "stem": "18061.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 329.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But outside, we didn't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't have themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They slept in-- in-- in February-- January, February.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They slept in street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't go in to take some apartments or tell people to go out [? of them. ?]",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the liberation, I was my home town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every place, every little street I went by, it was some kind of mix up in my mind, because I saw people [? was ?] who were relatives, which in my mind.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which actually, they were dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I left the place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got in touch with a few more barbers, and went back to that place I come from, Beuthen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we took over a barbershop and a beauty shop from a German woman, which she was willing, very, very willing to give it to us, and not to give to Poles or to give to Russian.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she worked over there with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that happened from February until up to June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, in Poland, it was created an army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Army [NON-ENGLISH] army, they call themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what they did is to kill Jewish people after the liberation, which a lot of Jewish people got killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Over 3,000 in Poland. 3,2000 Jewish people got killed after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It happened across the street where I-- I had the shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Two of them, officers, came in to a jewelry store without demanding anything, without taking anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just took out their guns and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, that time, to my wife, we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Same night, makes ready, and went to the German border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We maked our papers over there and went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Germany, we went to a place called before Baumberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- is in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
